trends: There have been 3 other sightings in Graham
There were no other sightings in Graham on or around April 16th 2013
Summary: Hovering Ufo above trees (100-250 ft.) White lights 2-3, hard to see bright light.
divs: sighting details1.)i was driving down next to road coming back from the store and i remember seeing the lights a week ago but a couple days in the night it wasn't there. 2.)i was looking around and say a bright object. 3.)airplane but it was not moving when i drove past it. 4.)the ufo\hovering object was not moving approx 150 ft. in the air over trees that are at least 100 ft. and the thing had 2-3 lights from it almost making it not possible to see. it looked like a future helicopter from a war movie with 2 engine things making it hover in the back. not moving at all. 5.)when i noticed it wasn't a plane or something i started to not think about it but i couldn't stop staring at it. my grandma was also freaking out so it wasn't just me. i was freaked out and still am a little here at home writing this now. 6.) i drove down my road to my house with the trees covering the sight of it.
